"1  (15-ounce) package refrigerated piecrusts","1  large egg, lightly beaten","1 1/4 cups firmly packed light brown sugar, divided","1 cup walnuts, finely chopped and toasted","3 tablespoons butter or margarine","1/4 teaspoon vanilla extract","1  (16-ounce) can pumpkin","1  (8-ounce) package cream cheese, softened","2  large eggs","2 tablespoons all-purpose flour","1 teaspoon ground cinnamon","1/2 teaspoon ground ginger","1/2 teaspoon ground allspice","1/2 teaspoon ground nutmeg","  Whipped cream (optional)"